uk.ac.aber.group14.model

Interface IPointOfInterest

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    PointOfInterest

    public interface IPointOfInterest
    This interface is used represent a point of interest. This will store a String name, String description, Location object, and optional String representing a picture associated with the point
